Note on Context:

This article is missing context, and therefore cannot be evaluated in full.

NOTE: Chris was not directly involved in this conversation.

This page will be for chats that have occurred exclusively between Bella and Fiona, most of which have happened during the Incest Saga. Bella's messages will be represented in fungus green, while Fiona's will be represented in magenta.

Notably, several of Bella's comments which appear in Fiona's screenshots are missing from Bella's own screenshots, suggesting Bella deleted several of her own messages.

Both Bella and Fiona released selected messages in fragments, often sending to other people first who then circulated the material. With little context such as dates to assist in piecing together the conversations, the texts are instead presented below as sorted by release batch.

Discussion of Incest Call

Unclear date, possibly 28 July 2021[note 2]

This is part of a conversation that Fiona and Bella had regarding a call with Chris, seemingly the Incest Call. This happened directly before the 4-minute leak of the full 4-hour call, which Fiona had made herself after Bella gave her a 9-minute version of this call. Judging by this, and posts from later conversations, it appears that Fiona had not yet had any access to the full recording before releasing the first leak, nor was she ever in the call itself.

The conversation also makes mention of Bella pushing for Chris and Fiona to have sex at Everfree Northwest, but didn't seem to discourage Chris from having sex with Barb.[7]

Fiona also claims that she had exposed herself to Chris, presumably on live video, and that Chris was turned on by this, indicating some degree of interest in her. The context in which this might have occurred is unknown. Also of note is how while Fiona was showing apparent shock at the idea that Chris was having sex with his mother, she also appears to still be on board with having sex with him, in spite of this. She also makes mention of the possibility of Chris being "swain away" from Barb after having sex with her.
